          "reviewBody": "I wish to deduct the one star too ..but it's impossible.....anyways ....teachers in this school are fabulous in teaching no doubt....except 2-3.....the main reason why I'm giving one star is .....their is lot of partiality between students and teachers......infact ....the principal of this school is so much worst....she should get the big tag of \"partiality\". No wonders why half of the nsb people hate her......this school could have been more better if the principal was changed....she doesn't know how to talk to parents properly until and unless they are from officers background....she insults students who are weak infront of everyone ,which 'can' affect the student's mental health. wish she was changed..... I'm ex student of this school...and literally....this school would have been better without this type principal..",
